parameters:
\n<Thief A>"Hah... That was something. It's been a while since I've let
out so much."

\n<Thief B>"Me too, me too. Seriously, I was wondering how it would go,
but who would've thought we'd get to screw a royal guard,
huh?"

\n<Thief B>"We'll never get another chance like this in our lifetimes.
Let's screw our brains out now, and once her ass is loose,
we'll quickly turn her into cash."

\n<Thief C>"...But where did that Riolaro guy take the soldiers, I
wonder?"

\n<Thief A>"Who knows? But hey, the woman we were after and the royal
guard are here. They'll be back soon enough."

\n<Thief A>"Until then, let's enjoy ourselves without any worries
(laughs)."
\n<Thief C>"Hehe, this is just too good..."
\n<Roselitte>"Why did I...! How could those men...! To me...!"

\n<Roselitte>"Damn it! Me...! To be made into such a miserable
laughingstock...!"

\n<Roselitte>"Shut up! I don't need your clumsy consolation! Are you
trying to mock me too!?"
Ameria gently placed her hand on Roselitte's arm.

\n<Ameria>"...Roselitte-san. If I were alone, I think I would be
terribly scared right now."

\n<Ameria>"Because you're here with me, I can keep from crying and
find the strength to keep going, you know?"

\n<Ameria>"There must be a chance to escape. So let's keep trying
together, okay? ...Right?"
\n<Roselitte>"...I'm sorry. I'm just a little tired..."

\n<Ameria>"It's okay, don't worry about it. Let's rest for a bit,
okay?"

parameters.name: 夜をイメージ・神秘的・不思議・ピアノ

parameters:
\n<Roselitte>"To involve civilians in this... I'm a disgrace as a royal
guard..."

\n<Ameria>"That's not true at all. You're not at fault, Roselitte-
san."

\n<Roselitte>"...When you were taken hostage, I abandoned you and tried
to kill Deorc."

\n<Roselitte>"And yet now, here I am being encouraged by you, supported
by you..."

\n<Roselitte>"...It's pathetic. I'm powerless. To think that I can't even
protect my own chastity..."

\n<Ameria>"...As a sister, it's natural for me to help those in
trouble."

\n<Ameria>"Roselitte-san, you tried to do the right thing, so please
don't be too hard on yourself, okay...?"

\n<Ameria>"Instead of blaming yourself, let's blame God! Why did you
let this happen-! ...like that"
\n<Roselitte>"...I'm not sure if that's appropriate for a Sister to say."

\n<Ameria>"Is that so? But Deorc said, 'I have been chosen by God,'
didn't he?"

\n<Ameria>"Then it's the God who allowed such things to happen who is
to blame! ...Isn't that right?"
\n<Roselitte>"...No, you're right. Indeed, all of this is God's fault."
The two exchanged glances and smiled faintly.

parameters.name: 陵辱系Hシーン【ベースが主役2】

parameters:
\n<Thief B>"...Hey, are we really gonna do this? Isn't it dangerous if
we get caught?"

\n<Thief C>"Shh. Don't raise your voice too much. You'll get us caught
by the others."
\n<Thief A>"Sorry to wake you up, eh?"

\n<Thief B>"Heh... We're not satisfied yet. Sorry, but you gotta
entertain us one more time."

\n<Thief B>"Whoa there, don't move. After being gang-raped like that,
and now unarmed, even you must find it tough, right?"

\n<Thief C>"Alright, let's get this over with quickly! Starting with
Roselitte!"
\n<Thief A>"Damn... damn it! The women are escaping, catch them!"
\n<Thief B>"Hey! Everyone, this is bad--!! The women are escaping--!!"
